question.title: MAUI Native android binding issues while compiling the app(Error:Unexpected attempt to initialize initialized java.lang.IllegalArgumentException. )
question.body:
MAUI Android native aar file binding project compile successfully after adding metadata but when the same project integrated into MAUI app it throws error while running the app.

The errors are like :

Invalid stack map table at instruction index 177: Error: Unexpected attempt to initialize initialized java.lang.IllegalArgumentException.  invokespecial Ljava/lang/IllegalArgumentException;<init>(Ljava/lang/String;)V,

Invalid stack map table at instruction index 176: Error: Unexpected attempt to initialize initialized terminalsdk.utility.ByteArrayWrapper.  invokespecial /terminalsdk/utility/ByteArrayWrapper;<init>([B)V,

What could be the reason

MAUI Binding project compile successfully but when the same project is referenced in Main MAUI app Project did not compile and throwing errors like Invalid stack map table at instruction index 176: Error: Unexpected attempt to initialize initialized

App should run successfully without errors.
